attributes.mlflow.spanInputs: {"prompt": "Create Cisco IOS XR 7.0.1 telemetry model-driven configuration to monitor CPU and memory operational utilization (processes and summary). Use gRPC with no TLS. Telemetry server 192.0.2.119 port 57500. Choose relevant sensor-paths."}
attributes.mlflow.spanOutputs:
"telemetry model-driven
 sensor-group CPU-MEMORY-UTILIZATION
  sensor-path /system-monitoring/cpu-utilization
  sensor-path /memory
 !
 destination-group DG-GRPC
  address-family ipv4
   destination 192.0.2.119
    port 57500
    encoding self-describing-gpb
    protocol grpc no-tls
 !
 subscription SUB-CPU-MEMORY
  sensor-group-id CPU-MEMORY-UTILIZATION sample-interval 30000
  destination-group-id DG-GRPC
 !"
